Package: snipe
Title: Initialise Targets Pipeline Around Data Objects
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Provides utilities for automatically creating a project structure designed for a targets pipeline. It handles data object relocation, directory setup, and initialises key R scripts for a seamless start in data analysis.
